{
  "texts": [
    "However, we soon noticed that many participants were much faster than this.",
    "We then adjusted the expected time of our survey slightly.",
    "For participants who finished the survey in under 20 min, we manually calculated the amount of time it would take to read the survey in its entirety at various reading speeds.",
    "Based on the results of Brysbaert (2019), we used 238 wpm as our \"average\" reading speed, and 500 wpm as a very fast reading speed.",
    "We excluded anyone who was completing the survey in less time than it would take to read it at between 400 and 500 wpm."
  ]
}